title: Is the destroyed Fukushima nuclear reactor about to fall into the ocean?
subtitle: Tebko, the company responsible for cleaning up after the Fukushima disaster in 2011, found high levels of radiation within a paralyzed reactor, but no reactor is about to collapse in the ocean.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A damaged nuclear reactor in Fukushima Daichi is about to fall into the ocean
